e":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T06:04:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我估係呢隻？<br />\n但四川based 中國人 成日full booking <br />\n台灣都好似有間呢類風格但唔記得名<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/24/135031_c52f85247330b8350902eae624d4f472.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F24%2F135031_c52f85247330b8350902eae624d4f472.jpg&h=7b7823c9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n台灣係咪無盡？好靚<br />\n但我要湊仔，所以一定要響香港紋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35aea82a8847c0bf56d14202e47e4a14d55f6e61","tid":478441,"uid":39694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T06:16:24.000Z","msg":"呢間專做卡通<br />\n但佢啲用色我個人唔係咁中意<br />\n好似唔夠實 好虛咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/24/141243_0c84c8d4b9a566f98f3468db212d8bab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F24%2F141243_0c84c8d4b9a566f98f3468db212d8bab.jpg&h=1d8ded14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢間就唔係專做卡通<br />\n但我中意佢啲色多啲<br />\n我之前都去搵佢紋左個<br />\n幾nice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/24/141557_c41c4f69bc25d82d9bdc865b58711723.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F24%2F141557_c41c4f69bc25d82d9bdc865b58711723.jpg&h=2b6d6f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇你中意邊個<br />\n2間都喺香港的"},{"pid":"25855b164206096a907cf7a4010099ef94666404","tid":478441,"uid":99189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T08:31:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢間專做卡通<br />\n但佢啲用色我個人唔係咁中意<br />\n好似唔夠實 好虛咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/24/141243_0c84c8d4b9a566f98f3468db212d8bab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F24%2F141243_0c84c8d4b9a566f98f3468db212d8bab.jpg&h=1d8ded14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢間就唔係專做卡通<br />\n但我中意佢啲色多啲<br />\n我之前都去搵佢紋左個<br />\n幾nice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/24/141557_c41c4f69bc25d82d9bdc865b58711723.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F24%2F141557_c41c4f69bc25d82d9bdc865b58711723.jpg&h=2b6d6f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇你中意邊個<br />\n2間都喺香港的</blockquote><br />\n我都有睇過，卡通畫係幾靚，但同感d色唔係太鐘意<br />\n又無乜漸變效果咁"},{"pid":"1c059cbc0b2206bc7212f0f165b185be72018819","tid":478441,"uid":99189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T08:33:27.000Z","msg":"最後問左Amazing，佢話ok<br />\n但見佢紋開大圖，唔知細圖得唔得<br />\n有無人響Amazing紋過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b88977b9090366d83ac8ed16553ed2fa1a2707","tid":478441,"uid":49457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T09:06:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最後問左Amazing，佢話ok<br />\n但見佢紋開大圖，唔知細圖得唔得<br />\n有無人響Amazing紋過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好紋太細, 老左好易花到一pat野"},{"pid":"1577fec56caac629691a4131e830a5e87c9f6942","tid":478441,"uid":99189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T09:27:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最後問左Amazing，佢話ok<br />\n但見佢紋開大圖，唔知細圖得唔得<br />\n有無人響Amazing紋過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好紋太細, 老左好易花到一pat野</blockquote><br />\n我都驚，但紋手腕3個圖，太大又無位同唔好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876d23151312030bff3c0989c40a9bb27b3fb553","tid":478441,"uid":150618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T09:37:31.000Z","msg":"Blackmoon<br />\n好野黎"},{"pid":"ff492bd7cc74fb11181b772549217b7cb1a50c70","tid":478441,"uid":73443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T09:40:33.000Z","m